data.description: Beautiful  home for sale in the Smithfield Section of the gated community of Brunswick Plantation.  Imagine sitting on your front porch enjoying the evening sunsets or the sunrises over the golf course across the street!  This three bedroom two bath home on a beautiful corner lot features a eat-in kitchen, formal dining area, living room with fireplace, entry foyer, full laundry room, master suite with ensuite and walk in closet.  Just off Master and living room, both with slider access, is a beautiful Carolina room with ez-breeze windows.  Then for outside living you have a large deck off of that.  Two car garage has a work bench area and walk up steps to attic storage!  The drive way is circular with two entrances.  Irrigation system installed in yard   Full living in this home!  New dishwasher, HVAC in 2018 Roof done in 2014. The sellers are also offering a home warranty so no worries when you move here!  Brunswick Plantation is  a beautiful tree lined gated community which features a championship golf course, Restaurants, indoor community pool and two outdoor community pools!  The community has a brand new clubhouse with fitness room, party/meeting rooms and your HOA contact holds an office there.  HOA fees are extremely reasonable at only $94.00 a month!  This is coastal living at best only a few miles from Sunset Beach, noted by National Geographic magazine as one the most beautiful beaches in the world.  Two international airports are less than 1 hour driving distance, all the activities of Myrtle beach just a short drive south and the City of Wilmington with its cultural activities only an hour north.   Put this on your list as a must see and join us under the beautiful Carolina Blue skies to ''Vacation where you live!''
